            </div>

            <div class='feat_card'>
              <span
                class='icon feat_icon'
                style="background-image: url('/svg/feature/canvas.svg')"
              ></span>
              <strong
                class='feat_card_title'
              >Canvas</strong>
              <a
                href='#'
                class='icon icon_arrow click feat_link'
              ></a>
            </div>

            <div class='feat_card'>
              <span
                class='icon feat_icon'
                style="background-image: url('/svg/feature/messaging.svg')"
              ></span>
              <strong
                class='feat_card_title'
              >Messaging</strong>
              <a
                href='#'
                class='icon icon_arrow click feat_link'
              ></a>
            </div>

            <div class='feat_card'>
              <span
                class='icon feat_icon'
                style="background-image: url('/svg/feature/accessibility.svg')"
              ></span>
              <strong
                class='feat_card_title'
              >Accessibility</strong>
              <a
                href='#'
                class='icon icon_arrow click feat_link'
              ></a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section class='page_section page_section_light_2'>
        <div class='page_content features_section_2'>

          <div class='features_section_2_text'>
            <h2 class='features_title'>What you need, when
              you need it</h2>
            <p
              class='features_descriptoin double_line'
            >Spend less time shuffling tabs with a
              comprehensive message archive and all your
              work tools at your fingertips.</p>

          </div>

          
            <div class='features_grid_3'>

              <div class='feat_card'>
                <span
                  class='icon feat_icon'
                  style="background-image: url('/svg/feature-2/apps.svg')"
                ></span>
                <strong>Apps and Integrations</strong>
                <p class='double_line'>Streamline work by connecting Slack with other services like
                    Google Drive, Office 365 and over 2,200 more.</p>
                <a
                  href='#'
                  class='icon icon_arrow click feat_link'
                ></a>
              </div>

              <div class='feat_card'>
                <span
                  class='icon feat_icon'
                  style="background-image: url('/svg/feature-2/builder.svg')"
                ></span>
                <strong
                  class='feat_card_title'>Workflow Builder</strong>
                <p class='double_line'>Automate routine actions and communication, so you can get
                    back to the kind of work only humans can do.</p>
                <a
                  href='#'
                  class='icon icon_arrow click feat_link'
                ></a>
              </div>

              <div class='feat_card'>
                <span
                  class='icon feat_icon'
                  style="background-image: url('/svg/feature-2/search.svg')"
                ></span>
                <strong
                  class='feat_card_title'>Search</strong>
                <a
                  href='#'
                  class='icon icon_arrow click feat_link'
                ></a>
              </div>

              <div class='feat_card'>
                <span
                  class='icon feat_icon'
                  style="background-image: url('/svg/feature-2/sharing.svg')"
                ></span>
                <strong
                  class='feat_card_title'>File sharing</strong>
                <a
                  href='#'
                  class='icon icon_arrow click feat_link'
                ></a>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
      </section>

        <section class='page_section page_section_deliveroo'>
          <div class="deliveroo">
            <div class="deliveroo_content">
              <h2 class="deliveroo_content_text">“The thing that keeps us connected
