                  prefer and enjoy using.”
              </h2>
              <a href="#" style="background-image: url('/img/deliveroo.png')" 
                class="deliveroo_content_badge click" src='/img/deliveroo.png' alt='deliveroo'>
              </a>
              <p class="deliveroo_content_signature">Will Sprunt, CIO, Deliveroo</p> 
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

